text = "Alright, here’s a fresh game idea you could realistically build as a 2D game

Game: “The Final Spark”

Core Concept:
You are the last robot remaining on Earth, an AI with unlimited power after humanity exhausted all energy resources. Desperate humans now chase you for your power, unaware that touching you delivers a deadly electric shock. Your objective is to survive for a set time while causing the fewest human casualties possible.

Would you like me to create the game for you?"
